{"word":"ἄκοπος","slug":"ἄκοπος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄκοπος</b></el> <p/><i>without weariness</i>, and so,<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <i>untired</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>not wearying</i>, of a horse, easy, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>removing weariness, refreshing</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}